	<br />
<div id="attachment_717024" style="width: 1600px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-717024" loading="lazy" src="https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-2.jpg" alt="" width="1600" height="1067" class="size-full wp-image-717024" srcset="https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-2.jpg 1600w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-2-425x283.jpg 425w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-2-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-2-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-2-1280x854.jpg 1280w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-2-1080x720.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px" /><p id="caption-attachment-717024" class="wp-caption-text">The new Giro Helios Spherical brings the most advanced version of MIPS down to a lower price point than before.</p></div></p>
<div id="attachment_717027" style="width: 1600px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-717027" loading="lazy" src="https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-3.jpg" alt="" width="1600" height="1067" class="size-full wp-image-717027" srcset="https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-3.jpg 1600w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-3-425x283.jpg 425w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-3-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-3-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-3-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-3-1280x854.jpg 1280w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-3-1080x720.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px" /><p id="caption-attachment-717027" class="wp-caption-text">The Giro Helios Spherical is anything but inexpensive, but it still costs a lot less than the top-end Aether.</p></div>
<div id="attachment_717030" style="width: 1600px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-717030" loading="lazy" src="https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-4.jpg" alt="" width="1600" height="1067" class="size-full wp-image-717030" srcset="https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-4.jpg 1600w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-4-425x283.jpg 425w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-4-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-4-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-4-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-4-1280x854.jpg 1280w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-4-1080x720.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px" /><p id="caption-attachment-717030" class="wp-caption-text">Even without the contrasting colors, the Giro Helios Spherical&#8217;s swooping lines makes for a distinctive-looking helmet.</p></div>
<div id="attachment_717036" style="width: 1600px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-717036" loading="lazy" src="https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-6.jpg" alt="" width="1600" height="1067" class="size-full wp-image-717036" srcset="https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-6.jpg 1600w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-6-425x283.jpg 425w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-6-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-6-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-6-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-6-1280x854.jpg 1280w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-6-1080x720.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px" /><p id="caption-attachment-717036" class="wp-caption-text">A closer look reveals the ball-and-socket design of the Giro Helios Spherical.</p></div>
<div id="attachment_717039" style="width: 1600px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-717039" loading="lazy" src="https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-7.jpg" alt="" width="1600" height="1067" class="size-full wp-image-717039" srcset="https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-7.jpg 1600w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-7-425x283.jpg 425w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-7-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-7-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-7-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-7-1280x854.jpg 1280w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-7-1080x720.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px" /><p id="caption-attachment-717039" class="wp-caption-text">Giro adds some color-matched reflective elements to both the front and rear edges of the Helios Spherical.</p></div>
<div id="attachment_717045" style="width: 1600px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-717045" loading="lazy" src="https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-9.jpg" alt="" width="1600" height="1067" class="size-full wp-image-717045" srcset="https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-9.jpg 1600w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-9-425x283.jpg 425w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-9-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-9-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-9-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-9-1280x854.jpg 1280w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-9-1080x720.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px" /><p id="caption-attachment-717045" class="wp-caption-text">The polycarbonate bridges on the Giro Aether (right) allow for wider and deeper internal channels than what you get on the Helios Spherical (left).</p></div>
<div id="attachment_717051" style="width: 1600px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-717051" loading="lazy" src="https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-11.jpg" alt="" width="1600" height="1067" class="size-full wp-image-717051" srcset="https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-11.jpg 1600w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-11-425x283.jpg 425w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-11-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-11-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-11-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-11-1280x854.jpg 1280w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-11-1080x720.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px" /><p id="caption-attachment-717051" class="wp-caption-text">The Roc Loc 5 retention system omits one or two features of the higher-end Roc Loc 5+, but it&#8217;s unlikely most people will notice the difference.</p></div>
<div id="attachment_717054" style="width: 1600px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-717054" loading="lazy" src="https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-12.jpg" alt="" width="1600" height="1067" class="size-full wp-image-717054" srcset="https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-12.jpg 1600w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-12-425x283.jpg 425w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-12-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-12-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-12-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-12-1280x854.jpg 1280w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-12-1080x720.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px" /><p id="caption-attachment-717054" class="wp-caption-text">The forward vents are well placed for storing your eyewear.</p></div>
<div id="attachment_717057" style="width: 1600px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-717057" loading="lazy" src="https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-13.jpg" alt="" width="1600" height="1067" class="size-full wp-image-717057" srcset="https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-13.jpg 1600w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-13-425x283.jpg 425w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-13-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-13-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-13-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-13-1280x854.jpg 1280w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-13-1080x720.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px" /><p id="caption-attachment-717057" class="wp-caption-text">The rubberized texture on the adjustment dial is a nice touch.</p></div>
<div id="attachment_717063" style="width: 1600px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-717063" loading="lazy" src="https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-15.jpg" alt="" width="1600" height="1067" class="size-full wp-image-717063" srcset="https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-15.jpg 1600w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-15-425x283.jpg 425w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-15-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-15-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-15-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-15-1280x854.jpg 1280w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-15-1080x720.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px" /><p id="caption-attachment-717063" class="wp-caption-text">The retention system is height-adjustable in four different positions.</p></div>
<div id="attachment_717066" style="width: 1600px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-717066" loading="lazy" src="https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-16.jpg" alt="" width="1600" height="1067" class="size-full wp-image-717066" srcset="https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-16.jpg 1600w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-16-425x283.jpg 425w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-16-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-16-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-16-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-16-1280x854.jpg 1280w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-16-1080x720.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px" /><p id="caption-attachment-717066" class="wp-caption-text">Interior padding is more generous on the Helios Spherical than it is on the Aether.</p></div>
<p><div id="attachment_717069" style="width: 1600px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-717069" loading="lazy" src="https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-17.jpg" alt="" width="1600" height="1067" class="size-full wp-image-717069" srcset="https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-17.jpg 1600w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-17-425x283.jpg 425w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-17-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-17-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-17-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-17-1280x854.jpg 1280w, https://cdn-cyclingtips.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giro-Helios-Spherical-17-1080x720.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px" /><p id="caption-attachment-717069" class="wp-caption-text">The strap sliders are a little more basic than I&#8217;d prefer to see at this price point, but they nevertheless seem to stay put.</p></div><br />
